### How to Use

Use the navigation bar at the top to select different modes of analysis. Most tools allow you to choose a **Source Dataset (D1)** and a **Comparison Dataset (D2)**. 

- **D1 → D1 / D2 → D2:** Internal conceptual distances within a single source.
- **D1 → D2:** Cross-linguistic or cross-source evaluation (e.g., English Human vs. Italian Human).

If you use this tool in your research, please cite the original work by Lynott et al. (2020), Wingfield & Connell (2023) and the present study by Ciria et al. (2026).

